## Fleet Observations

The 57-repo audit revealed 6 emergent patterns:
1. Doc debt accumulates at the frontier (newest code = worst docs)
2. Natural tiering emerges without design
3. Extracted knowledge forms static sediment layer
4. Fleet services converge to shared infrastructure
5. Quality spectrum is wide (and healthy)
